{"tid":2164728,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"【10分鐘搞掂】速剪店格價懶人包","createTime":"2020-08-19T10:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T18:27:45.000Z","uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"99f86bc0dac09b5599d8cea23c9e36077855bfb2","tid":2164728,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T10:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/F4Uvq9gzbHBm32mqf2Ug6A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-09/35d12fa0-cd20-11e9-bb66-5bbf3003c04d\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FF4Uvq9gzbHBm32mqf2Ug6A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F35d12fa0-cd20-11e9-bb66-5bbf3003c04d&h=2909a582&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n速剪文化傳入香港都有好幾年，唔少速剪店都累積一定口碑，同埋已經有完善既分店網絡、固定收費套餐，甚至提供剪髮以外服務。Yahoo著數專員今次從價錢、服務、衛生度幫大家挑選出幾間比較出色既速剪店，方便大家選擇～<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/DCO7R5DKK7fp4ypo.rs9iQ--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-09/35e023c0-cd20-11e9-bcf6-9998dc5a63d4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FDCO7R5DKK7fp4ypo.rs9iQ--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9MTI4MDtoPTk2MA--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F35e023c0-cd20-11e9-bcf6-9998dc5a63d4&h=7ce991a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1. QB House<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.linkhk.com/linkweb/api/file/_C/ShopPhoto/tny1c2/TNY1_LG07.jpg?v=7ecb8dc4a7f140480f68213805306c62\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkhk.com%2Flinkweb%2Fapi%2Ffile%2F_C%2FShopPhoto%2Ftny1c2%2FTNY1_LG07.jpg%3Fv%3D7ecb8dc4a7f140480f68213805306c62&h=8af72027&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n由日本傳入香港既QB House，正正就係掀起速剪文化既開山祖師！QB House係日本公司，所以衛生俾到人一定信心，每次剪髮都會用自家原創既梳，每個剪髮位置都有自己一部消毒機，就算潔癖既朋友都剪得放心。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：$70<br />\n<br />\n分店數量：全港29間，主要位於鐵路沿線<br />\n<br />\n2. 15M PLUS<br />\n<img src=\"https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2019-09/36526d90-cd20-11e9-9fa5-993b7525bb56?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=9092ce6e6e17055045692adcf5738bb5&amp;oe=5D878B55\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2019-09%2F36526d90-cd20-11e9-9fa5-993b7525bb56%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D9092ce6e6e17055045692adcf5738bb5%26oe%3D5D878B55&h=aba37da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n15M係一間由香港人開既速剪店，店鋪主要位於屋苑商場，都好方便街坊，而且15M亦都會將剪刀同電剷等工具用酒精消毒，同埋用UV紫外線消毒殺菌箱存放理髮工具，衛生方面亦有保證。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：$50<br />\n<br />\n分店數量：全港11間<br />\n<br />\n3. SC Center日式單剪專門店<br />\n<img src=\"https://speedcutcenter.com/image/branch11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fspeedcutcenter.com%2Fimage%2Fbranch11.jpg&h=c42a6869&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSC Center引入日式速剪店營運模式，同樣都係只提供單剪服務，但價錢就比較平～SC Center都幾重視員工質素，只聘請年資最少5年、有專業髮型屋工作經驗既理髮師傅。除咗用速剪店必備既紫外光消毒機消毒工具之外，理髮師傅剪髮前，都會用酒精搓手液清潔雙手。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：$50<br />\n<br />\n分店數量：全港10間<br />\n<br />\n4. X-CUT LAB 單剪專門店<br />\n<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn%3AANd9GcRdolDYqKLPnDE0ZJlhVM-_F9jMaWWhPxjWLw&amp;usqp=CAU\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fencrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com%2Fimages%3Fq%3Dtbn%253AANd9GcRdolDYqKLPnDE0ZJlhVM-_F9jMaWWhPxjWLw%26usqp%3DCAU&h=28d1caa9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nX-CUT LAB網上好評算多，另外都歡迎女士去速剪，除咗滿65歲長者有剪5次送1次優惠，間中亦會推出優惠～XC LAB同樣用具都經消毒酒精和紫外線消毒機雙重消毒，貼近日式速剪既服務水平。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：$60<br />\n<br />\n分店數量：全港11間<br />\n<br />\n5. GB Color<br />\n<img src=\"https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/Kw5hqqFH0ASnh9UfEgqSZvpSqf9kr-2UhyZK2wTyMrfd3gVJMwia3o-ec2A_6wyhjdtvsFp7E94iuEJK=w768-h768-n-o-v1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flh3.googleusercontent.com%2FKw5hqqFH0ASnh9UfEgqSZvpSqf9kr-2UhyZK2wTyMrfd3gVJMwia3o-ec2A_6wyhjdtvsFp7E94iuEJK%3Dw768-h768-n-o-v1&h=e9170b44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔少人都有自己買染髮劑返屋企自己染髮，而GB color單剪以外既平價染髮服務，就照顧到佢地需要。GB color既染髮服務，可以照顧上年紀需要遮蓋白髮既朋友～不過長頭髮去GB color染髮會比短髮貴，女士們就要多加留意。<br />\n<br />\n價錢：單剪$50起；染髮$150起<br />\n<br />\n分店數量：全港6間"},{"pid":"2114b6f726bb1584137394cc4317d91ad227532e","tid":2164728,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:26:14.000Z","msg":"呢度5間嘢 我附近一間分店都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3abbd3bf79002c89e1753ce2ec0a7882534eea94","tid":2164728,"uid":47132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2114b6f726bb1584137394cc4317d91ad227532e","tid":2164728,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T15:26:14.000Z","msg":"呢度5間嘢 我附近一間分店都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T10:17:35.000Z","msg":"qb都冇？"},{"pid":"0b8a962053cbd6bd86c72fe06c3adc276727f119","tid":2164728,"uid":190187,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T13:51:45.000Z","msg":"Qb而家垃圾到 鳩鏟就得 想靚千其唔好去"},{"pid":"0b74d29d8285b5911c9d6f3866fafd6983a6110b","tid":2164728,"uid":4846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-21T18:27:45.000Z","msg":"Sc果張圖寫60蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但個表同篇文寫50蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}